    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/921ff6c4fd61e24cc5eb2adfabd2a4c3.avif?t=1771929935\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras_big/921ff6c4fd61e24cc5eb2adfabd2a4c3.avif?t=1771929935 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《海盗崛起》聚焦于扩张和发展。在战役中，开局时你只有一艘小船和一把硬币。你需要完成任务并寻找宝藏，建立自己的经济地位并与其他派系交往。你也可以选择战斗，登上或击沉其他船只以获取战利品。组织你的船队和船员，承担最具挑战性的任务，比如占领兵力强度和布局各异的岛屿。在大规模海战中击败大型殖民舰队，猎杀海盗，寻找遗失已久的宝藏，探索充满危险的神秘世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/22e43e3c09135018802479ec6abd0daf.webp?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/4d6e5044935f6720b3ba093d7ea1fa4a.poster.avif?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/4d6e5044935f6720b3ba093d7ea1fa4a.webm?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/4d6e5044935f6720b3ba093d7ea1fa4a.mp4?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>不靠程序生成，由人工打造的数百种环境。《海盗崛起》中的一切都经过精心打造，会为你提供一种新的体验和挑战。完全可破坏的环境和建筑使你可以利用舰队炮击远程夷平一座岛屿。你可以与定居点长官和舰队船长交谈，发现隐藏的地点，也可以靠自己探索和调查找到它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/8d704796bfe8656dc1a6d30782f84b6d.webp?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/dbd4a53bc7e2ea9fcddba3e2318e609e.poster.avif?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/dbd4a53bc7e2ea9fcddba3e2318e609e.webm?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/dbd4a53bc7e2ea9fcddba3e2318e609e.mp4?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>海盗生涯充满选择。世界各地分布着200种以上可供贸易的商品，港口有独特的贸易路线和商人。你需要为舰队添置商船，最大化你的运输潜力。与其他势力建立关系，提升你的贸易效率。参与战争、狩猎赏金或寻找隐藏的宝藏也是积累财富的手段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/638d723974240324c8ef674f32ec7b99.webp?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/b03fe6292621d61c446386765fe23fe5.poster.avif?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/b03fe6292621d61c446386765fe23fe5.webm?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/b03fe6292621d61c446386765fe23fe5.mp4?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>深层次的外交系统允许所有派系之间发展关系。你需要与遭遇的每一个派系交往。人工智能派系间会以战争争夺资源，力量均衡的改变会伴随着战舰活动的增加和贸易路线的封锁，从而影响你的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/c7793b01d3bd033f78717a1507c4ec47.webp?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/d79e0ab5eedb2913000f85e76be2532b.poster.avif?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/d79e0ab5eedb2913000f85e76be2532b.webm?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/d79e0ab5eedb2913000f85e76be2532b.mp4?t=1771929935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>用1600年-1900年间的30种以上可玩船只组成你的舰队，从轻快的卡拉维尔帆船到火力凶猛却笨拙的120炮风帆战列舰。酒馆是个雇佣船员的好地方。让你的战舰拥有专业船员，派他们登上敌方船只，或是登陆夺岛以获取被动收入。敌对行动会对派系关系产生影响，海盗猎人舰队会不断寻求赏金。战役难度将动态提高，无论玩家变得多强大，都会感受到挑战性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1400660/extras/aa217d008265d108bd60def352535542.webp?t=1771929935\" width=600 height=50 /></span>进入竞技场，进行团队或个人战斗。选择你的船只，扬长避短，击沉敌人。</p>",
